'''天主教庫里蒂巴總教區'''（{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Curitibensis}}；{{lang-pt|Arquidiocese de Curitiba}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[巴西|巴西]]的一個教省[[總教區|總教區]]，下轄六個教區。

總教區位於[[巴拉那州|巴拉那州]]東南部，教座位於首府[[庫里蒂巴|庫里蒂巴]]，2006年時有1,480,046名教友，佔轄區總人口65.4%。教區下轄129個堂區，有426名司鐸。現任總主教為{{link-en|若瑟·安多尼·佩魯佐|José Antônio Peruzzo}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e Nomine, 07.01.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/01/07/0010/00021.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200508163418/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/01/07/0010/00021.html |archivedate=2020-05-08 |language=it |date=2015-01-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為{{link-pt|伯多祿·安多尼·馬爾謝蒂-費達爾托|Pedro Antônio Marchetti Fedalto}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=RINUNCE E NOMINE, 19.05.2004 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/05/19/0247/00809.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2020-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200508163715/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2004/05/19/0247/00809.html |archivedate=2020-05-08 |language=it |date=2004-05-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

教區於1892年4月27日成立<ref name="dio">[http://www.archive.org/stream/sanctissimidomi04xiiigoog#page/n68/mode/2up Bolla ''Ad universas orbis''], in ''Sanctissimi Domini nostri Leonis papae XIII allocutiones, epistolae, constitutiones aliaque acta praecipua'', Vol. V (1891-1894), Bruges 1897, pp. 56-65</ref>，1926年5月10日升為總教區<ref>{{cite book |title=ACTA APOSTOLICAE SEDIS |volume=XIX |year=1927 |publisher=Typis Polyglottis Vaticanis |pages=81-85 |url=https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-19-1927-ocr.pdf |accessdate=2020-04-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200409173428/https://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS-19-1927-ocr.pdf |archivedate=2020-04-09 |language=la |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

